{"about_the_game":"<strong>Desert Kingdoms 2</strong> is a minimal medieval real-time strategy game.<br><br>In the desert there are only a few <strong>waypoints</strong> that can be settled. <br>Conquer these and expand settlements there. <br>Destroy the other kingdoms and become the sole ruler of the desert.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/dk2_gif1.gif?t=1730477888\" /><br><br>Manage resources like wood, stone and iron, develop villages, and conquer enemy kingdoms in procedurally generated skirmish maps.<br>Develop cities to build large buildings, like <strong>Siege Workshops</strong>. <br>So you can tear enemy kingdoms apart.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/dk2_gif2.gif?t=1730477888\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2>* <strong>Skirmish mode</strong> with <strong>procedurally generated</strong> maps<br>* Different <strong>unit types</strong> with strengths and weaknesses<br>* Develop villages with different <strong>buildings</strong><br>* <strong>Pause</strong> the game at any time if it gets too hectic or <br>* <strong>speed up time</strong> if you're waiting for something.<br>* <strong>Develop</strong> your settlements from a small hamlet to a village to a city.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/dk2_gif3.gif?t=1730477888\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hamlet \u2013 Village \u2013 Town</h2><strong>Hamlet</strong> small settlement with a few building sites where basic resources can be mined<br><br><strong>Village</strong> more space for buildings and special resources. Can mine advanced resources.<br><br><strong>City</strong> Space for large buildings, but unable to mine resources<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956730/extras/dk2_gif4.gif?t=17304778